FINANCIAL CONSULTANT
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 07:50:05
Ref. JB2971264
Job Description
A limited number of new openings are now available for
professionals to begin a career in Abu Dhabi, the most successful region of our 72 worldwide offices.
ON TARGET FIRST YEAR EARNINGS OF 600,000 AED
Our highly professional consultants help the growing number of expats within the UAE make the most of the tax free high earning environment whilst helping to achieve their ultimate goals.
As a consultant you have access to our providers who are world leading institutions such as JP Morgan, Morgan Stanley and Goldman Sachs. Our clients have exclusive access and tailor made solutions unavailable anywhere else.
Successful candidates will be required to consult with potential clients on how to utilise our services, find the best solution, help maximise tax free earnings and future growth.
Full training and qualifications are provided for the financial aspects of the position.
Skills
If you have some of these attributes then we want to talk to you:
Motivated, top performer, wants a new challenge, competitive, professional, honest, top communicator,
relationship builder.
Areas of expertise required are either financial services, senior sales, business development, account management, client relationship management, sales management, mortgage advisor, real estate, insurance, consultative sales.
This job is posted in the following Specialties:
